Archiver
A small utility that creates a zip file off of the entire project directory, erasing the .git and doc directories which might make the submission too heavy for submit.cs. erasing the .git directory which might make the submission too heavy for submit.cs. Execute as Java application.
CollisionResolver
CollisionResolver is an enum which provides named constants for four of the most widely used collision resolution techniques in hash tables:
HashTable
HashTable is an abstraction over hash tables which store String keys and map to String values.
KVPair
KVPair is a simple abstraction of a <String, String< pair.
KVPairList
KVPairList is a simple linked list storing pairs of Strings.
KVPairListTests
KVPairList is a small jUnit - based test suite for KVPairList.
LinearProbingHashTable
LinearProbingHashTable is an Openly Addressed HashTable implemented with Linear Probing as its collision resolution strategy: every key collision is resolved by moving one address over.
NoMorePrimesException
NoMorePrimesException is a simple RuntimeException which is thrown whenPrimeGenerator has run out of primes to generate.
OpenAddressingHashTable
OpenAddressingHashTable is an abstract class that models openly addressed hash tables, i.e hash tables which store the key-value pairs within the table itself instead of using the table to store pointers to separate buckets.
OrderedLinearProbingHashTable
OrderedLinearProbingHashTable is an Openly Addressed HashTable implemented with Ordered Linear Probing as its collision resolution strategy: every key collision is resolved by moving one address over, and the keys in the chain is in order.
Phonebook
Phonebook is an abstraction over phonebooks: databases of < Full Name, Phone Number> pairs.
PrimeGenerator
PrimeGenerator is a simple immutable class which stores and retrieves prime numbers.
PrimeGeneratorTests
A jUnit testing framework for PrimeGenerator.
Probes
Probes is a class that contains information about the efficiency of an operation, in terms of probes that the code had to "pay" to finish the operation (successfully or not).
QuadraticProbingHashTable
QuadraticProbingHashTable is an Openly Addressed HashTable which uses Quadratic Probing as its collision resolution strategy.
SeparateChainingHashTable
SeparateChainingHashTable is a HashTable that implements Separate Chaining as its collision resolution strategy, i.e the collision chains are implemented as actual Linked Lists.
StudentTests
StudentTests is a place for you to write your tests for Phonebook and all the various HashTable instances.
UnimplementedMethodException
A simple RuntimeException subtype which is used by skeleton code to notify students that a certain method needs to be implemented.
